  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Invite groups to share how their strategies compared to those of their partner groups.</li>
      <li>Invite partner groups to share their comparisons with the whole class using 
        <q>how much less</q>  and 
        <q>how much more</q>  statements.
      </li>
    </ul>
